HEADWORD: Stateliness
<hw>State"li*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of being
stately.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>For <qex>stateliness</qex> and majesty, what is comparable to a
horse?</q> <rj><qau>Dr. H. More.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stately</ent>⟦br⟧
